say much to him
about Rudy Sr.,

135
00:12:00,573 --> 00:12:02,410
because I don't
know what to say.

136
00:12:02,410 --> 00:12:05,482
And I don't know if
I should just let him

137
00:12:05,482 --> 00:12:07,654
