194
00:15:31,260 --> 00:15:32,463
(SIGHS)

195
00:15:42,349 --> 00:15:44,053
Okay. Uh...

196
00:15:45,122 --> 00:15:46,992
I'll call you tonight.

197
00:15:55,475 --> 00:15:57,045
